      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owners. The engine runs smoothly and starts reliably every time, providing a dependable driving experience. The exterior is clean with only minor signs of regular use, and the interior has been maintained nicely with no major wear or tear. It\u2019s a solid, road-ready car that offers a great balance of performance and comfort for its next owner.",
