      "description": "Step into luxury with this stunning vehicle that looks like it just rolled off the assembly line! It is in absolute mint condition, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that still has that new-car feel. Meticulously cared for and maintained to the highest standards, this car offers a pristine driving experience for its next lucky owner.",
