    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available is a 2003 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Alpine White, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement and a recent cooling system overhaul. Suspension geometry remains true, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup for exceptional turn-in response. The interior shows minor bolster wear, and the exterior retains a deep luster despite typical road-use patina. A mechanically sorted, driver-focused machine that delivers 333 hp with linear precision.",
