    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a beautifully maintained 2018 executive sedan that perfectly blends sophisticated styling with spirited performance. The exterior is finished in a timeless metallic charcoal that still holds a deep, impressive shine. While the body is straight and free of any major blemishes, there are a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from standard use, which are only noticeable upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is a testament to careful ownership. The black leather seats are soft and free of cracks or thinning, and the cabin retains that clean, fresh scent of a non-smoker vehicle. Every button and feature\u2014from the heated seats and premium surround-sound system to the intuitive touchscreen navigation\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in great shape. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and a full multi-point inspection already completed. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts with precision, and the suspension remains firm yet comfortable. It sits on a set of high-quality all-season tires with significant tread life remaining. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle ready for its next owner to drive away with total peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
